e 10|line L10]] <ref name=\"planbcn\">{{cite web | url = http://w20.bcn.cat/GuiaMap//default.aspx#x=26371&y=80231&z=5&c=K001&w=1380&h=830&base=GuiaMartorell | title = Pl\u00e0nolbcn | publisher = Ajuntament de Barcelona | language = Catalan | accessdate = 2015-02-03}}</ref><ref name=\"tmap\">{{cite web | url = http://cartometro.com/cartes/metro-tram-barcelona/ | title = Track map of the Barcelona Metro | publisher = cartometro.com | accessdate = 2015-02-03}}</ref> and is located between [[Proven\u00e7ana (Barcelona Metro)|Proven\u00e7ana]]  and  [[Foc Cisell (Barcelona Metro)|Foc Cisell stations]] in the southern part of the city. The station is located underneath the ''Passeig de la Zona Franca''.\n\n[[File:Foneria ascensor.png|thumb|centre|Elevators that connect platforms with the lobby]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{commonscat-inline|Foneria metrostation}}\n\n{{Barcelona Metro line 10}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Foneria (Barcelona Metro)}}\n[[Category:Barcelona Metro line 10 stations]]\n[[Category:Transport in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 2018]]\n\n\n{{Spain-railstation-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox station\n| name            = Foneria\n| type            = [[Barcelona Metro]] [[rapid transit]] station\n| style           = \n| image           = foneria andana.png\n| image_caption   = Upper platform of the station\n| address         = Passeig de la Zona Franca with Carrer de Foneria, [[Barcelona]]\n| country         = \n| coordinates     = {{coord|41|21|38|N|2|08|18|E|region:ES-CT_type:landmark_source:kolossus-nlwiki|display=inline,title}}\n| line            = \n| other           = \n| structure       = Underground\n| platform        = \n| depth           = \n| levels          = \n| tracks          = \n| parking         = \n| bicycle         = \n| baggage_check   = \n| opened          = 2018\n| closed          = \n| rebuilt         = \n| electrified     = \n| ADA             = \n| code            = \n| owned           = 